<MILESTONE N="6"> <NOTE N="&dagger;" PLACE="foot"><HI>Luke</HI> xii. 1.</NOTE> And Je&s;us &s;aid to them, Take heed and beware of the leaven of the Phari&s;ees and Sadducees. 
