and how many ba&s;kets ye took up? <MILESTONE N="11"> How do ye not under&s;tand, that I &s;pake not to you con|cerning bread, to beware of the leaven of the Pha|ri&s;ees 
and Sadducees? <MILESTONE N="12"> Then they under&s;tood, that he did not bid <HI>them</HI> beware of the leaven of bread, but of the doctrine of the Phari&s;ees and Sadducees.</P>
<P><MILESTONE N="13"> <NOTE N="&Verbar;" PLACE="foot"><HI>Mark</HI> viii. 27. <HI>Luke</HI> ix. 18.</NOTE> And Je&s;us coming into the coa&s;ts of Ce&s;area Philippi, a&s;ked his di&s;ciples &s;aying, Whom do 
