up his cro&s;s and follow me. <MILESTONE N="25"> <NOTE N="&dagger;" PLACE="foot">C.x. 39. <HI>Mark</HI> viii. 35. <HI>Luke</HI> ix. 24. xvii. 33. <HI>John</HI> xii. 25.</NOTE> For who&s;oever will &s;ave his life, &s;hall lo&s;e it, and who&s;oever will lo&s;e 
