and &s;trewed <HI>them</HI> in the way. <MILESTONE N="9"> And the multitudes that went before and that followed after cried, &s;aying, Ho&s;unna to the Son of David; ble&s;&s;ed in the name of the Lord <HI>is</HI> he that cometh: Ho&s;anna in the highe&s;t.</P>
