<MILESTONE N="26"> But if we &s;ay, Of men; we fear the multitude: 
for all hold John as a prophet. <MILESTONE N="27"> And they an&s;wer|ing &s;aid to Je&s;us, We cannot tell. And he &s;aid to them, Neither tell I you, by what authority I do 
