that ye might believe him. <MILESTONE N="33"> <NOTE N="*" PLACE="foot">Mark <HI>xii.I.</HI> Luke <HI>xx. 9.</HI></NOTE> Hear another pa|rable. There was a certain hou&s;holder, who plant|ed a vineyard, and hedged it round about, and digged a wine-pre&s;s in it, and built a tower, and let it out to hu&s;bandmen, and went into a far coun|try. 
<MILESTONE N="34"> And when the &s;ea&s;on of fruit drew near, he
