<MILESTONE N="38"> <NOTE N="&Dagger;" PLACE="foot"><HI>Mark</HI> xv. 27. <HI>Luke</HI> xxiii. 32.</NOTE> Then were two robbers crucified with him, one on the right-hand and one on the left.</P>
<P><MILESTONE N="39"> And they that were pa&s;&s;ing by reviled him, 
wagging their heads and &s;aying, Thou that de|&s;troye&s;t the temple, and builde&s;t <HI>it</HI> in three Days, &s;ave thy&s;elf. <MILESTONE N="40"> If thou be the Son of God, come 
