<HI>him,</HI> and &s;ent <HI>him</HI> away empty. <MILESTONE N="4"> And again he &s;ent to them another &s;ervant: and at him they ca&s;t &s;tones, and wounded <HI>him</HI> in the head, and &s;ent <HI>him</HI> 
