and in&s;cription? They &s;ay to him, Ce&s;ar's. <MILESTONE N="17"> And Je&s;us an&s;wering &s;aid to them, Render to Ce&s;ar the
<PB N="188" REF="023976_0187_0FC2A237815B9478">things that are Ce&s;ar's, and to God the things that are God's. And they marvelled at him.</P>
<P><MILESTONE N="18"> <NOTE N="&Verbar;" PLACE="foot"><HI>Mat.</HI> xxii. 23. <HI>Luke</HI> xx. 27.</NOTE> Then come to him the Sadducees, who &s;ay there is no re&s;urrection, and they a&s;ked him, &s;ay|ing, 
