<P><MILESTONE N="28"> <NOTE N="&dagger;" PLACE="foot"><HI>Mat.</HI> xxii. 34. <HI>Luke</HI> x. 25.</NOTE> And one of the &s;cribes coming to him, hav|ing heard them di&s;puting together, <HI>and</HI> perceiving that he had an&s;wered them well, a&s;ked him, Which
