is the fir&s;t commandment of all? <MILESTONE N="29"> And Je&s;us an&s;wer|ed him, The fir&s;t commandment of all <HI>is,</HI><NOTE N="&Dagger;" PLACE="foot">Deut. <HI>vi. 4.</HI></NOTE> Hear, 
