<P><MILESTONE N="35"> <NOTE N="*" PLACE="foot"><HI>Mat.</HI> xxii. 41. <HI>Luke</HI> xx. 41.</NOTE> And Je&s;us an&s;wering, as he taught in the temple, &s;aid, How &s;ay the &s;cribe<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">, that Chri&s;t is 
