<P><MILESTONE N="38"> <NOTE N="&Dagger;" PLACE="foot"><HI>Mat.</HI> xxiii. 5. <HI>Luke</HI> xx. 46.</NOTE> And he &s;aid to them in his teaching, Beware of the Scribes, who love to walk in long robes, 
