<P><MILESTONE N="41"> <NOTE N="&Verbar;" PLACE="foot"><HI>Luke</HI> xxi. 1.</NOTE> And Je&s;us &s;itting over-again&s;t the trea&s;ury, beheld how the people ca&s;t money into the trea&s;ury: 
