<P><MILESTONE N="18"> <NOTE N="&Verbar;" PLACE="foot"><HI>Mat.</HI> xvi. 13. <HI>Mark</HI> viii. 27.</NOTE> And as he was praying apart, his di&s;ciples were with him. And he a&s;ked them &s;aying, whom 
