<P><MILESTONE N="28"> <NOTE N="&dagger;" PLACE="foot"><HI>Mat.</HI> xvii. 1. <HI>Mark</HI> ix. 2.</NOTE> And about eight days after the&s;e &s;ayings, he took Peter and John and James, and went up into 
