buy one. <MILESTONE N="37"> For I &s;ay to you, That this which is written mu&s;t yet be accompli&s;hed in me,<NOTE N="*" PLACE="foot">I&s;aiah <HI>liii. 12.</HI></NOTE> And he was numbered with the tran&s;gre&s;&s;ors. For the 
things concerning me have an end. <MILESTONE N="38"> And they &s;aid, Lord, behold here <HI>are</HI> two &s;words. And he &s;aid to them, It is enough.</P>
<P><MILESTONE N="39"> <NOTE N="&dagger;" PLACE="foot"><HI>Mat.</HI> xxvi. 30.</NOTE> And going out, he went, according to <HI>his</HI> cu&s;tom, to the mount of Olives, and his di&s;ciples 
