into temptation. <MILESTONE N="41"> And he was withdrawn from
<PB N="307" REF="023976_0306_0FC2CAF89D26B520">them about a &s;tone's ca&s;t, and kneeling down, 
he prayed, <MILESTONE N="42"> Saying, Father, if thou art willing, remove this cup from me: neverthele&s;s not my 
will, but thine be done. <MILESTONE N="43"> And there appeared to him an angel from heaven &s;trengthening him. 
<MILESTONE N="44"> And being in an agony he prayed more earne&s;tly: and his &s;weat was as it were great drops of blood 
