&s;hining garments. <MILESTONE N="4"> And as they were afraid, and bowed <HI>their</HI> face to the earth, they &s;aid to them, 
Why &s;eek ye the living among the dead? <MILESTONE N="5"> He is 
not here, but is ri&s;en. <MILESTONE N="6"> Remember how he &s;pake
