<PB N="317" REF="023976_0316_0FC2CB20CF5EC4C8">
<MILESTONE N="34"> &s;aying, The Lord is ri&s;en indeed, and hath ap|peared 
to Simon. <MILESTONE N="35"> And they told the things <HI>done</HI> in the way, and how he was known by them in the breaking of bread.</P>
<P><MILESTONE N="36"> <NOTE N="*" PLACE="foot"><HI>Mark</HI> xvi. 14.19. <HI>John</HI> xx. 19.</NOTE> And as they &s;pake thus, Je&s;us him&s;elf &s;tood in the mid&s;t of them, and &s;aith to them, Peace <HI>be</HI> 
